2::0::followers as well as nobles.  A necromancer looks upon a bloody
2::0::battlefield strewn with the dead as a potential army waiting to be
2::0::trained.
2::0::
2::0::Advanced necromancers wield fierce powers, manipulating evil Runes
2::0::to effect their will upon the world, and making pacts with demons
2::0::to obtain power in return for souls.
2::0::
2::0::With great power also comes great danger, and necromancy is the most
2::0::dangerous of the magical arts.  Only those willing to risk death at
