2::0::Knowledge of 9591 causes a character to keep its faction affiliation
2::0::secret.  Other units attempting to learn the what player the unit
2::0::belongs with the skill Determine character's lord [9521] will fail.
2::0::
2::0::Permissions set for the player of a character concealing its faction
2::0::affiliation will not include the character.  For example, suppose
2::0::unit [5499] is concealing the fact that it belongs to player [613].
2::0::Permissions declared for player [613] (such as ADMIT, DEFEND, etc.)
2::0::will not include the sneaky unit [5499], since [5499] will not admit
2::0::to an affiliation with [613].
2::0::
2::0::Furthermore, such units will not DEFEND units from their own faction
2::0::by default, since this might reveal their identity.
