2::0::Train angry peasants~[9592]
2::0::---------------------------
2::0::
2::0::Usage:  TRAIN 23 [days]
2::0::        TRAIN 10 [days]
2::0::Time:   as given
2::0::
2::0::The noble employs persuasive means to rouse mild-tempered peasants
2::0::into a state of anger.  Angry peasants fight with twice the attack
2::0::value of regular peasants.  However, in their excited state they
2::0::are untrainable to any other kind of man.
2::0::
2::0::Examples:
2::0::
2::0::	train 23	# train all peasants to angry peasants
2::0::	train 23 5	# train five peasants into angry peasants
2::0::	train 10	# calm all angry peasants back into peasants
2::0::
2::0::Angry peasants require a monthly maintenance cost of 2 gold each.
