2::0::Conceal self~[9593]
2::0::-------------------
2::0::Usage:  USE 9593 <flag>
2::0::Time:   three days
2::0::
2::0::This skill allows a character to conceal itself from view.
2::0::When activiated, other characters will not see the unit in their
2::0::location reports, and will not see the unit come and go.
2::0::
2::0::The unit must be alone in order to conceal itself.  It may not be
2::0::stacked with any other characters, or possess any followers, such
2::0::as peasants, soldiers, workers, etc.  It may also not be the first
2::0::character inside a sublocation, building or ship.  The owners of
2::0::these small locations are always visible.
2::0::
2::0::Hiding takes three days to accomplish.  However, turning off
2::0::concealment takes zero time.
2::0::
2::0::Use of the skill will set whether or not the unit is trying to
2::0::hide from view:
2::0::
2::0::	use 9593 1	# Hide from view, takes three days
2::0::	use 9593 0	# Don't conceal self from view, zero days
2::0::
2::0::Note that attempts to gain entrance to buildings or ships with
2::0::the MOVE order will subject to the unit to the ADMIT system.
2::0::A failure to gain entrance with MOVE will give the unit away to
2::0::the structure's owner.
